Package com.SCHSRobotics.HAL9001.system.gui.viewelement.eventlistener

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AdvancedListener
    An interface that gives EventListeners the ability to be more selective about which events they handle via CriteriaPackets.
    EventListener
    The base interface implemented by all EventListeners.
    UniversalUpdater
    A special interface that allows event listeners that implement it to handle all events in the event heap.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EntireViewButton
    A menu button that takes up the entire screen.
    ViewButton
    A menu button that can be made to run tasks on certain click events.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    HandlesEvents
    An annotation for event listeners that specifies what types of events will be handled.
